{"tid":1625080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇求各位手足唔好忘記印尼女記者","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:53:44.000Z","uid":124636,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1f9f69e1b33373575ceb5bc5cc48b4f81d322c","tid":1625080,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"9.29全球反極權大遊行，有位依幾個月幫我地香港人報導真相嘅印尼語報紙《SUARA》女記者Veby Mega Indah，比黑警用橡膠子彈射盲右眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家仲記得嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OmPzjpwt2JA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOmPzjpwt2JA&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=f1500f59\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OmPzjpwt2JA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191002/s00001/7aadca7a95ac3d2c154c17a92166a6f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191002%2Fs00001%2F7aadca7a95ac3d2c154c17a92166a6f7.jpg&h=dd3c385c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我要今日開post提番起，因為由今日開始就係印傭姐姐放假嘅高峰期，佢地會出去聚會。既然之前有手足做左個印尼文嘅文宣去講件事，我地係咪要做d野呢？<br />\n<br />\n爆眼女記者印尼文文宣！！同我推爆佢！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615021</a><br />\n<br />\n可能你會話印尼領事館跪左，你想connect印尼都connect唔到，但唔好輕視印傭姐姐嘅政府壓力，外傭姐姐係印尼國家其中一個重要外匯收入來源嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算真係造唔到為印尼領事館製造壓力嘅結果，印傭姐姐可能為做狗嘅主人d狗糧加料呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個亦都係我之前開個post嘅其中一步，國際戰線就係咁玩。<br />\n前大學教授：短期運動方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612046</a>"},{"pid":"eae61a667cad01fe88bc407bf86fad96dc32947e","tid":1625080,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879567a201b8e703650d2cf6483731a0112292d5","tid":1625080,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:50:27.000Z","msg":"推 極嚴重"},{"pid":"cd1cef4c86b0b1483df165a920b9bd352f9f9122","tid":1625080,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"有無有心人可以落區同印傭溝通吓<br />\n想佢地知道香港人好撐佢地<br />\n我地好想幫中槍記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84573817cc6edd50e186c55306c8dab31437711","tid":1625080,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f6bee4c89ee2dac2080edbfefb5b1f2747341bd","tid":1625080,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"4d6b730c61cc0ead557bc7707e3503fa9f9123c0","tid":1625080,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1cef4c86b0b1483df165a920b9bd352f9f9122","tid":1625080,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"有無有心人可以落區同印傭溝通吓<br />\n想佢地知道香港人好撐佢地<br />\n我地好想幫中槍記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"各手足自己去番自己住嘅社區啦，大家一定知道d姐姐會喺邊度聚集"},{"pid":"6a625980aae415bd28d63dc0c06d3fc1419ea6ec","tid":1625080,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"5ad654abd65995717ce4becd003c88444fe1fd00","tid":1625080,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"fcb5778abf34f81c692ae1149395861d49ab66ac","tid":1625080,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFOVt8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A